opulation: in the first century after the Conquest it was the commonest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Guillaume DE CHATEAUNEUF-RANDON II was born in 1130. He had at least 1 son with Marquèze DU MAS DE GROSFAUX. He died after 1175."},"et":{"1130–après 1175":"1130–pärast 1175","1120–1175":"1120–1175","1155–1185":"1155–1185","1130–1175":"1130–1175","environ 1155":"umbes 1155","après 1175":"pärast 1175","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","1120":"1120","1130":"1130","1185":"1185","Aft 1175":"pärast 1175","Estables, Mende, Lozère, Occitanie, France":"Estables, Lozère, Occitanie, Prantsusmaa","Châteauneuf-de-Randon, Lozère, Languedoc-Roussillon, France":"Châteauneuf-de-Randon, Lozère, Languedoc-Roussillon, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1130–après 1175":"1130–1175 jälkeen","1120–1175":"1120–1175","1155–1185":"1155–1185","1130–1175":"1130–1175","environ 1155":"noin 1155","après 1175":"1175 jälkeen","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","1120":"1120","1130":"1130","1185":"1185","Aft 1175":"1175 jälkeen","Estables, Mende, Lozère, Occitanie, France":"Estables, Lozère, Occitanie, Ranska","Châteauneuf-de-Randon, Lozère, Languedoc-Roussillon, France":"Châteauneuf-de-Randon, Lozère, Languedoc-Roussillon, Ranska"},"fr":{"1130–après 1175":"1130–après 1175","1120–1175":"1120–1175","1155–1185":"1155–1185","1130–1175":"1130–1175","environ 1155":"environ 1155","après 1175":"après 1175","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","1120":"1120","1130":"1130","1185":"1185","Aft 1175":"après 1175","Estables, Mende, Lozère, Occitanie, France":"Estables, Lozère, Occitanie, France","Châteauneuf-de-Randon, Lozère, Languedoc-Roussillon, France":"Châteauneuf-de-Randon, Lozère, Languedoc-Roussillon, France","lifeSummary":"Guillaume DE CHATEAUNEUF-RANDON II est né en 1130. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Marquèze DU MAS DE GROSFAUX. Il est décéd